
'''* Report: The clean energy transformation: a new paradigm for social progress within planetary boundaries. Nafeez Ahmed. Club of Rome, Earth4All, 2022'''

URL = https://www.clubofrome.org/publication/earth4all-ahmed/


=Description=

"As part of the Earth4All project, collaborators have submitted deep-dive papers to delve further into the issues and solutions needed to transform our economic system and provide an equitable future for all on a finite planet. This paper explores new possibilities that could empower humanity to solve some of its most intractable problems: energy scarcity and volatility, the persistence of food insecurity and malnutrition, global poverty, and widening inequality."


